f\colon \mathbb R^2\rightarrow\mathbb R,(x,y)\mapsto\sin x\cdot\cos y
M>0
(x,y)\in\mathbb R^2
T_2
2
|f(x,y)-T_2(x,y)|\leq M(|x|+|y|)
T_2
|x|+|y|
|R_3(x,y)|\leq M(|x|+|y|)
T_2(x,y)
 T_2(x,y) = x. 
 \Big| f(x,y)-T_2(x,y)\Big|= \Big| \sin(x)\cos(y)-x\Big|= \Big| \sin(x)\cos(y)-\sin(x)+\sin(x)-x\Big|
 \leq |\sin(x)(\cos(y)-1)|+|\sin(x)|+|x| 
 =|(\cos(y)-1)|+2|x| 
 \leq |y|+2|x|  
 \leq 2(|x|+|y|). 
 |\sin(x)|\leq |x|,\quad |\cos(y)-1|\leq |y| 
